WaterMaskPage说明引入属性

WaterMaskPage

说明

頁面脱敏水印组件

引入

npm install water-mask
import { WaterMaskPage } from 'water-mask-page';

基础用法

这里是需要脱敏背景的内容区域
<img src={Demo} />
<div style={{ width: '200px', height: '200px', border: '1px solid red' }}>
  <WaterMaskPage
    color="red"
    fontSize={15}
    width={100}
    height={100}
    content="你好"
  >
    <div style={{ height: '200px', width: '200px' }}>
      这里是需要脱敏背景的内容区域
    </div>
  </WaterMaskPage>
</div>

属性

fontSize
number | undefined
color
string | undefined
content
string
required
width
number | undefined
height
number
required
opacity
number
required
feedHeight
number | undefined
rotate
number | undefined
zIndex
number | undefined
textAlign
"left" | "center" | "end" | "right" | "start"
required
textBaseline
"middle" | "alphabetic" | "bottom" | "hanging" | "ideographic" | "top"
required
